    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと事務所に戻って来られた\n後はメールを返して、それと……あれ、mihoさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… finally back at the office.\nJust need to reply to emails‚ and… oh‚ miho?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8299476357,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2903.3856976,
          "startTime": 7.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3670.0523642,
          "startTime": 8.4999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。今掃除中で邪魔なので\nさっさとどいていただけると助かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. I'm cleaning right now‚ so you're in the way.\nIt would be helpful if you could move aside quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼しました……あれ、mihoさんが\n事務所の掃除をしてくれてたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-My apologies… Wait‚ miho‚\nhave you been cleaning the office?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "いつも沙季が整頓してくれているようですが\n子供にばかりやらせるのも大人として情けないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Usually Saki seems to keep things tidy‚\nbut letting a child do it all feels pathetic as an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "いくら片付けても、いつの間にかまた散らかって……\n今日なんて、雑誌が読み散らかされていましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how much I clean‚ it's messy again in no time…\nEven today‚ magazines were left scattered after being read.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……その雑誌、俺が読んでたやつです……\n以後整理整頓を徹底いたします、はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… those magazines are the ones I was reading…\nI'll make sure to keep things organized from now on‚ yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル達の模範となるべきマネージャーが\n率先して堕落していてどうするんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A manager‚ who should be a role model for idols‚\nshouldn't be the one leading the way in laziness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それにアイドル誌に混じって車の雑誌もありましたけど\n業務中に何をやっていたんですか、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ there was a car magazine mixed with the idol ones.\nWhat exactly were you doing during work hours‚ honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}